title: Kingpin
description:
The Kingpin is a fictional character and a crime lord that appears in the comic books published by Marvel Comics. The character first appears in The Amazing Spider-Man #50 (July 1967), and was created by writer Stan Lee and artist John Romita, Sr.

This torrent contains a 7 issue mini-series of Kingpin published by Marvel Comics in 2003. Enjoy and Seed.
